title: Tot mom Casey Anthony’s ‘other victims’
itunes:title: Tot mom Casey Anthony’s ‘other victims’
description:
Casey Anthony appears to blame her parents — specifically her father — for the death of her two-year-old daughter in a new interview with the Associated Press. She tells the AP reporter that she doesn’t know what happened to Caylee, but that the child was in the care of her parents. Nancy Grace believes George and Cindy Anthony are the Tot Mom’s “other victims.”
